data.description: Stunning home located in the desirable Kenly Farms community. Create memories w/ family & friends in the spacious great room featuring trendy Wainscotting accent wall, upgraded baseboards, built-in speakers, granite kitchen counter tops, stainless steel appliances, and tons of storage. The downstairs bedroom & full bath is perfect for guests or hobbies. There is plenty of space out back to relax or entertain under the inviting pergola, extended patio and lush green grass. Rejuvenate in the oversized primary bedroom featuring ample natural light, vaulted ceiling, and large closet. The laundry room, under stair closet, and 3 car garage provides convenience and extra storage. Recent upgrades include, hot water heater, 1 A/C unit, exterior & interior paint, attic insulation, and sealed home for energy efficiency.  Welcome home!
